description: Even the choosiest foodies can’t help but be wooed by the menu at Susy’s Soup & Deli, which includes a slew of the tastiest soups you’ll ever spoon into. Chicken Noodle, Tomato Tortellini, Lobster Bisque, and Potato Cheese are only a few, and they’re all super yummy - just ask any Clevelander their point of view. You’ll also find divinely delicious sandwiches, salads, and wraps, too. So when you see Suzy’s truck roaming through any avenues near you, know that you’re in for some “Woohoo!”-worthy food.
name: Susy's Soup & Deli
